                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="Teacher_name"><span style="color:red;">*</span>班級導師：</label>
                            <input id="teacher_name" type="text" name="Teacher_name" required>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="Teacher_phone"><span style="color:red;">*</span>聯絡方式(建議留班級導師電話)：</label>
                            <input id="phone_num" type="tel" name="Teacher_phone" required>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="Email_address"><span style="color:red;">*</span>Email：</label>
                            <input id="email" type="email" name="Email_address" pattern="[A-z0-9._%+-]+@@[a-z0-9.-]+(\.[a-z]{2,})+$" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="image_upload">
                            <b>
                                <p>
                                    <span style="color:red;">*</span>上傳檔案：
                                </p>
                            </b>
                            <div class="custom-file mb-3">
                                <input type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="customFile" name="filename" accept="image/*" required>
                                <label class="custom-file-label" for="customFile">選擇檔案</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="image_preview">
                            <span><b>預覽圖：</b></span>
                            上傳進度
                            <span id="main-thread-progress"></span>
                            <p id="main-thread-log"></p>
                            <img id="preview-after-compress" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="right_image">
                        <img src="~/images/keyvision.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <label for="Work_concept">作品理念(200字以內，非必填)：</label>
                <p class="wordsNum">還剩下200個字可以輸入</p>
                <textarea id="thought" name="Work_concept" placeholder="輸入文字" maxlength="200"></textarea>
                <p>備註：本活動將於每日定時進行人工審核及更新作品，因此作品上傳後並非立即公布作品，再請耐心等候。若有任何問題請來電詢問 (02)2776-6133 #103</p>

                <div class="policy_box">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="policy" required>
                    <label for="policy">我已詳閱<a href="#anchor">肖像與隱私權政策並同意</a></label>
                </div>

                <div class="submit_button">
                    <input type="submit" id="submit" name="SubmitWork" value="確認提交" asp-controller="WorkCollect" asp-action="ProvePrint">
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/browser-image-compression@1.0.17/dist/browser-image-compression.js"></script>
